A father murdered two of his children early Friday morning as they lay sleeping in their beds before turning the gun on himself after arguing with his wife.

David Mohney shot three of his children, Savanna, 14, David, 11, and a Lauren, 9, after a fight with his wife Cynthia in their Port Orange, Florida, home.

Savanna and David have died, and Lauren, who is in critical condition, has been upgraded to stable condition.

